      "name": "index.ts",
      "filePath": "packages/antd-vue-pro/src/components/component-provider/index.ts",
      "summary": "component-provider 模块入口文件，导入 ProComponentProvider 组件并作为默认导出，同时导出 ComponentVars 类型供外部使用。",
      "tags": ["barrel", "entry-point", "type-export"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:packages/antd-vue-pro/src/components/form/components/BaseForm/index.vue",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "index.vue",
      "filePath": "packages/antd-vue-pro/src/components/form/components/BaseForm/index.vue",
      "summary": "ProForm 配置驱动表单组件，使用泛型约束表单实例类型，支持字段联动、嵌套字段、自定义组件、网格布局和动态插槽，通过 provide 注入表单实例，模板中将配置通过 BaseFormItem 递归渲染。",
      "tags": ["form", "config-driven", "vue-component", "generic", "slot-teleport"],
      "complexity": "moderate",
      "languageNotes": "使用 Vue 3 generic 属性实现泛型组件，F extends Form<any> = Form 约束表单数据类型推导"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:packages/antd-vue-pro/src/components/form/components/BaseFormItem/index.vue",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "index.vue",
      "filePath": "packages/antd-vue-pro/src/components/form/components/BaseFormItem/index.vue",
      "summary": "BaseFormItem 表单字段递归渲染组件，将字段配置数组渲染为实际表单项，支持字段分组（嵌套 fields 触发自身递归）、网格布局控制、FormItem 包装校验、组件绑定（通过 BaseField）及插槽透传。",
      "tags": ["form-item", "recursive", "config-driven", "vue-component", "grid-layout"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:packages/antd-vue-pro/src/components/form/components/index.ts",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "index.ts",
      "filePath": "packages/antd-vue-pro/src/components/form/components/index.ts",
      "summary": "表单内部组件集 Barrel 文件，集中导出 BaseForm、BaseFormItem、BaseField、ContainerFragment、SlotComponent 组件及其 Props/Instance 类型定义。",
      "tags": ["barrel", "component-export", "type-export"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:packages/antd-vue-pro/src/components/form/index.ts",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "index.ts",
      "filePath": "packages/antd-vue-pro/src/components/form/index.ts",
      "summary": "表单模块公共 API 入口，按分类组织导出：组件包装与类型（ContainerFragment 等）、组件映射类型（ComponentMap）、表单 Schema 类型（Field/Fields）及核心 Hooks（useForm、useFields 等）。默认导出 BaseForm 组件。",
      "tags": ["barrel", "entry-point", "public-api", "form-module"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:packages/antd-vue-pro/src/components/table/components/BaseTable.vue",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "BaseTable.vue",
      "filePath": "packages/antd-vue-pro/src/components/table/components/BaseTable.vue",
      "summary": "ProTable 配置驱动表格组件（331行），集成了搜索表单（SearchForm）、分页、列控制（ColumnControl）、尺寸切换（SizeControl）、序号列注入、插槽系统（search-form/button-bar/toolbar/table）及全局配置注入，通过 useTable hook 管理表格状态。",
      "tags": ["table", "config-driven", "search", "pagination", "vue-component"],
      "complexity": "complex",
      "languageNotes": "使用 Vue 3 generic 属性实现泛型表格组件，T extends Table<any> = Table 约束表格数据类型；使用 defineModel 双向绑定 size 和 loading；模板中通过 ContainerFragment 动态切换包裹容器"
    },
