      "type": "function",
      "name": "ProForm",
      "filePath": "packages/antd-vue-pro/src/components/form/components/BaseForm/index.vue",
      "lineRange": [1, 90],
      "summary": "配置驱动表单组件，使用泛型 F 约束表单实例类型，接收 form 实例和 grid 网格配置，通过 provide 注入表单对象，渲染 Ant Design Vue Form 并委托 BaseFormItem 递归渲染字段列表，同时支持以字段 path 命名的动态插槽透传。",
      "tags": ["form", "config-driven", "generic", "provide-inject", "slot-teleport"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "function:packages/antd-vue-pro/src/components/form/components/BaseFormItem/index.vue:BaseFormItem",
      "type": "function",
      "name": "BaseFormItem",
      "filePath": "packages/antd-vue-pro/src/components/form/components/BaseFormItem/index.vue",
      "lineRange": [1, 156],
      "summary": "表单字段递归渲染组件，遍历 fields 配置数组，通过 PathProvider 提供路径上下文，GroupedFieldAttrs 解析分组属性，对嵌套 fields 递归渲染自身，叶子字段委托 BaseField 渲染具体控件，支持网格布局和 FormItem 校验包装。",
      "tags": ["recursive", "grid-layout", "form-rendering", "field-mapping"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
